<b>About Us</b>
<br /><br />
We know you&rsquo;ve worked hard to network and get top grades for your dream summer job, but that&rsquo;s only half the journey. Now you need to find your perfect summer accommodations so you can sip cocktails on your rooftop under the moonlight after work. Founded by students at Yale and the University of Pennsylvania, SubLite provides an easy solution to finding the perfect summer sublet for university students across the United States. SubLite is an exclusive student-to-student platform for listing and discovering sublets to complement summer internships. Unlike other housing platforms, all our users are verified using their school email addresses. Say goodbye to horror housing stories!
<br /><br />
<b>How It Works</b>
<br /><br />
We work with universities committed to assisting students with the summer internships to subscribe to the site on their students&rsquo; behalf. Only students with verified emails will be able to create profiles. Hosts create listings for the space they are offering to sublet. Our enhanced search functionality captures the essence of an ideal sublet for university students: proximity to workplace, public transportation options, price per week, and privacy. Once a sublet hunter has found an ideal space, he or she simply contacts the host by email and works out a deal – we trust you to decide on the terms and payment directly!
